Encode-Safename

An encoding for safe filenames.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module or script
with the perldoc command.

    perldoc Encode::Safename
    perldoc safename

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Encode-Safename

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Encode-Safename

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Encode-Safename

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Encode-Safename/

